      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Payments Overview\nBusiness-event panels in this dashboard are backed by the payment custom telemetry already emitted by the payment initiation, webhook, reconciliation, and fulfillment flows.\n\n### Queryable payment events today\n- `payment.initiated`\n- `payment.webhook.received`\n- `payment.webhook.persisted`\n- `payment.webhook.persistence_failed`\n- `payment.reconciliation.confirmed`\n- `payment.reconciliation.failed`\n- `payment.credit_wallet`\n- `payment.wallet.created`\n- `payment.wallet.credited`\n- `payment.activate_subscription`\n- `payment.subscription.activated`",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Current Payment Event Scope",
      "type": "text"
    },
